com.ibm.team.repository.common.query.ast

Interface ISelectionElement

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IAggregateFunction, IBooleanField, IBooleanLiteral, IDateTimeField, IDateTimeLiteral, IEnumField, IEnumLiteral, IField, ILiteral, INumericField, INumericLiteral, INumericScalarFunction, IPseudoVariable, IScalarFunction, IStringField, IStringLiteral, IStringScalarFunction, IUUIDField, IUUIDLiteral

    public interface ISelectionElement
    Selection elements are query elements that are valid elements for selection in an IDataQuery. For example, instances of IField are valid for selection while instances of IInputArg are not.
    Since:
    0.5
    See Also:
    IDataQuery, IDataQuery.select(ISelectionElement)
